overview: The user initiated a request for thorough browser-based testing of the
  application. The agent systematically navigated through the application,
  testing the questionnaire flow, form validation, report generation, PDF
  download, and admin login functionality. During this process, the agent
  encountered and debugged several issues, including unexpected navigation
  behavior and the "Pre-fill & Jump to Report" button not immediately jumping to
  the report. It also identified ESLint warnings and an outdated page title.
  Following the testing, the agent implemented fixes for the identified issues,
  including updating the page title, enhancing various questionnaire sections,
  improving the comprehensive sleep health analysis in the report (both web and
  PDF), and expanding the CSV export. All changes were committed in 8 atomic,
  logically grouped commits.
